:" the Administrator of the Small Business Administration in accordance with paragraph (1);"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcfcafac7-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2199/b/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an assessment as to whether these measures have successfully ensured that only qualified HUBZone small business concerns are participating in the HUBZone program under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s657a"},"text":"section 657a of title 15","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcfcafac8-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2199/b/2/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an assessment as to whether the reforms made by the criteria and guidance implemented under paragraph (1) have resulted in job creation in the Commonwealth of Puerto Rico; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcfcafac9-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s2199/b/2/E"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"E"},"text":"(E)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" recommendations on how to improve controls in the HUBZone program.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcfcafaca-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/187/tIV/s412"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–187, title IV, § 412","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/595"},"text":"130 Stat. 595","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n